2 THAT the Senate recognize the importance and practice of good dental
3 health, especially in children, to ensure the well-being of generations to
4 come in the State of Arkansas and designate the month of February as National
5 Children's Dental Health Month.
6
7 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that upon adoption, a copy of this resolution be
8 presented to the leaders of Delta Dental Plan of Arkansas and the Delta
9 Dental of Arkansas Foundation, Inc., by the Secretary of the Senate.
